(5, 1, 'Android Phone', 'Android is an operating system developed by Google for mobile devices such as smartphones and tablets. It&#039;s known for its flexibility, customization options, and wide range of devices from various manufacturers. Android offers a diverse app ecosystem through the Google Play Store, where users can download apps, games, and utilities tailored to their preferences. It supports a variety of hardware configurations and integrates well with Google services like Gmail, Google Maps, and Google Assistant.', 1, '2025-01-28 17:16:02'),
