(7, 2, 'Air Pods', 'AirPods are Apple&rsquo;s wireless Bluetooth earbuds, designed for seamless integration with Apple devices like iPhones, iPads, Macs, and Apple Watches. They offer high-quality audio performance, an ergonomic design for a comfortable fit, and advanced features such as automatic device pairing, touch controls, and voice activation with Siri. With their compact charging case, AirPods provide extended battery life and are perfect for listening to music, taking calls, or accessing virtual assistants on the go. Some models, like the AirPods Pro and AirPods Max, also include active noise cancellation and spatial audio for immersive sound experiences.', 1, '2025-01-28 21:25:13');

